624
00:56:43,680 --> 00:56:47,760
♫Keeping you close, just by my side♫

625
00:56:47,800 --> 00:56:51,520
♫I'm sorry I once was so heartless and cold♫

626
00:56:51,560 --> 00:56:55,880
♫The truth is I love you
